UKaMadiba umangaze abaningi ekhwela edilika kubantu ethi basukela umyeni wakhe, bacabanga ukuthi uyafika kwipolitiki. Umama wesizwe ubetholakala ngaphansi kwegama elithi Firstladyzuma kodwa manje usezibiza ngo-tobeka_madiba_zuma_is_her_name. Umbhalo wakhe wacasula abaningi ababemgxeka njengoba abhala ukuthi “Kusazoshuba.......ungalwi nomuntu engalwi nawe...” Abanye bambuza ukuthi usho ukuthini uma ekhuluma kanjena wagcina ngokuphendula ethi “Kusazoshipha ukotshi Darling”. Ngemuva kwale mibhalo u-Edward Zuma oyindodana kaMengameli wakhipha isitatimende egxeka inkulumo kanina wathi ayehlanga kahle futhi wathi bayaziqhelelanisa nayo.